data.description: Just minutes from town, yet private enough to feel like you're off the beaten path! This beautiful home nestled in the foothills of the smoky mountains has been well taken care of, and is ready for its new owners! 3 bedroom plus BONUS room, 2 bath with an amazing, private master bathroom! There's also a separate office space!  New metal roof! New back deck and LARGE front deck to enjoy grilling, relaxing, OR put your own hot tub! Owners reinforced decking to accommodate installing a hot tub!  The living space is great for hosting guests with its open concept. The fireplace is wood burning and just the right amount of cozy for those chilly nights! Storage shed also on the property. Enjoy the freedom of having this unrestricted acreage in the county! Would be a great investment property to add to your portfolio as well!
